track_title: Winding Stair, Rough, and Simmons Mountains

track_notes: This is an on-trail hike beginning at the campground.  We took a wrong turn early on near the campground, so this track includes a little extra - it should be obvious where.  Beautiful forest hike!  We also continued on to activate Rough Mountain W5O/OU-006, further down along the same trail.
track_title: Winding Stair Mountain via Ouachita National Trail
